    "user_id": "U002ELAINE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "😕",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Also — Marcus called out. We're short at the front desk until noon.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T02:36:04+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "🙏",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Can you cover or do you need me to pull someone? Don't want you stretched before the meeting even starts.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T02:37:04+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002ELAINE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "💪",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I've got it. My sister Pat was planning to stop by around 10 but I'll push her to lunch. She won't mind.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T02:38:04+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "🙏",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "You sure? That's a long morning. Say the word and I'll come down.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T02:39:04+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002ELAINE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "😄",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I'm fine, honestly. Lobby's quiet. And Pat married Kevin Harrison — she knows better than most that plans shift. 😄",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T02:40:04+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "❤️",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Fair point. Thank you, Phil. Really.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T02:41:04+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002ELAINE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "👀",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Phil did Elaine say anything after the 7:15 this morning? Had to run for that 8am checkout and missed the tail end.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:47:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "😮",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Big wedding block coming in Friday. 22 rooms, party out of Burlington — the Hendersons. Elaine wants both of us on at 3.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:48:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003NANCY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "😬",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "22 rooms 😬 are we doing staggered check-ins or just praying?",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:49:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "😅",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Just praying, mostly. She said 4pm hard cutoff on early arrivals. I give it until noon before someone's standing at my desk with luggage.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:50:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003NANCY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "🚚",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "ok fair. hey was that Brian's truck in the lot yesterday afternoon? the blue one?",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:51:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "😂",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Yeah he stopped in. Returned my pie dish from Easter, stayed about ten minutes, told me I looked tired. Classic.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:52:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003NANCY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "☕",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "lol he means well. want me to grab you a coffee from Mocha Joe's before my shift? I'm walking past anyway.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:53:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "😄",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Half-and-half drip, please. You'll be my favorite colleague. Don't tell the others.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-26T11:54:55+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003NANCY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "👀",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Phil did Elaine say anything after the 7:15 this morning about the new check-in policy? I had to run before she finished up",
