    "ts": "2025-12-24T16:40:10+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "👍",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Contactless checkout going to all rooms by August. That was the main thing.",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-24T16:41:10+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004AMY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "🥵",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "ugh August is so soon. did she mention the lobby AC at all? it was 78° at the front desk yesterday, I was melting",
    "thread_ts": "1702828800.000100",
    "ts": "2025-12-24T16:42:10+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "👍",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "She didn't bring it up. I'll flag it with her tomorrow — she's usually in after the 9 o'clock rush.",
