    "ts": "2025-12-24T16:44:10+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "❤️",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "That was Colleen. She was up in Brattleboro for the weekend and stopped in on her way through.",
